descriptionHtml:
Download the grocery app that gives you more for less and enjoy being first to know about Food Basics flyer deals and exclusive coupon offers.

- Weekly coupons on big brands
Spend less time coupon cutting and more time doing the things you love with convenient coupons redeemable at checkout via smartphone.

Discover always more for less wherever you are with a Food Basics store finder in your pocket!

title: Food Basics

creator: Metro Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the super app Food Basics, the ideal tool for all fans of practical, fast and economical grocery shopping.

Get access to thousands of products, exclusive offers and coupons, weekly flyers and more.

With its rethought design and numerous personalized tools, the Food Basics app will simplify your daily life.

YOUR IN-STORE GROCERY
Save both time and money in-store.
- Browse through the weekly flyer with ease, discover the very best specials, and take advantage of the current promotions to save big.
- Find the Food Basics that’s closest to you. Then, access information and services offered by the store.
- Easily find the products you're looking for in your Food Basics app using the product locator.

FOR Moi Rewards MEMBERS
Enjoy all the benefits of your Moi Rewards program.
- Consult coupons tailored to your tastes and add them with a single click.
- Always have your Moi Rewards card on hand.
- Earn and redeem points easily.
- Manage your account, including your personal information, your cards, and your order history, with ease.

Loving our app? Give it 5 stars!
